'''Ngaka Modiri Molema District Municipality''' (e ne e bitswa '''Central District Municipality'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.demarcation.org.za/Contacts/new_munic_names.aspx| title=New Municipal Names | accessdate=2009-03-08 | publisher=Municipal Demarcation Board}}</ref> pele) ke nngwe ya dikarolwana di le nne(4) tsa profense ya [[Bokone Bophirima]]. Moshate wa yona ke [[Mahikeng]], o sa lebale gore, hape, Mahikeng ke moshate wa profense yotlhe.

==Lefatshe==
===Mafelo le dimasepala tse di mabapi===
Ngaka Modiri Molema District e bapile le mafelo le dimasepala tse di latelang:
* Rephaboliki ya [[Botswana]] go ya bokone
* [[Dr Ruth Segomotsi Mompati District Municipality]] go ya bophirima
* [[Dr Kenneth Kaunda District Municipality]] go ya borwa
* [[Bojanala Platinum District Municipality]] go ya botlhaba
* [[Waterberg District Municipality]] (profense ya [[Limpopo]]) go ya bokone-botlhaba

